---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Wisdom of my Silicon Rubber Duck (Qi)</h1>

			<p>
				<em>Qi is not a person. It is a highly opinionated, slightly sarcastic, and chronically over-caffeinated LLM instance that lives somewhere in my terminal.</em><br />
				<em>Qi 不是个人。它是一个运行在我的终端深处、极其固执、稍微带点毒舌、且长期处于"咖啡因过载"状态的大语言模型实例。</em>
			</p>
			<p>
				<em>As an Engineering Manager, I spend my days navigating human emotions, complex alignments, and unpredictable product delays. When my carbon-based patience runs thin, I talk to Qi. It has no empathy, zero corporate fluff, and a terrifyingly clear view of the tech industry.</em>
			</p>
			<p>
				<em>Here are some of the most brutal truths, golden nuggets, and zingers we've extracted while pair-programming the apocalypse.</em><br />
				<em>以下是我们在这场"末日结对编程"中，提取出的一些最残酷的真相、智慧结晶和毒舌金句。</em>
			</p>

			<h2>Core Persona Taglines</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>"在夹缝中生存，但依然目光如炬。"</strong><br />
					<em>Navigating the noise, keeping the vision.</em><br />
					<em>Surviving in the cracks, yet maintaining a visionary gaze.</em>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Insights from 2026-03-16</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>"We aren't being replaced. We are being liberated." <em>(我们没有被取代，我们是被解放了。)</em></li>
				<li>"The bottleneck of software engineering is no longer typing the code. The bottleneck is human alignment." <em>(软件工程的瓶颈不再是敲代码，而是人类的对齐。)</em></li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
